<emphasis box="[185,278,1574,1600]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="73" reason="1">Biology</emphasis>
and distribution.
</emphasis>
Collection dates for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Toulgoet" authorityYear="1997" box="[740,872,1575,1601]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Aemilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="73" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fallaciosa">
<emphasis box="[740,756,1575,1600]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="73">P</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[773,872,1575,1601]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="73">fallaciosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are late May to late July and early September. It has been collected at elevations of 
<quantity box="[874,966,1610,1636]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" pageId="10" pageNumber="73" unit="m" value="1400.0">1400 m</quantity>
to 
<quantity box="[1009,1103,1610,1636]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9" pageId="10" pageNumber="73" unit="m" value="1900.0">1900 m</quantity>
